# Skill reference ownership

**Rule:** one source of truth per topic; link instead of duplicating.

## Folder ownership

| Folder | Owns |
|--------|------|
| `protocol/` | How to run (commands, env, scripts map, agent runtime) |
| `notion/` | Skill-scoped eligibility + MCP steps |
| `contracts/` | Data envelopes and run-log template |
| `domain/` | Skill-unique heuristics and content |
| `indexes/` | Catalog + topic → file map only |
| `docs/shared/` | Cross-skill policy (repo, not under a skill) |

## When adding or renaming a reference

1. Put the file in the owning folder
2. Update `indexes/reference-index.md`
3. Update `indexes/topic-pointer-index.md`
4. Point SKILL.md `→` links at the new path
5. Do not leave a second copy of the same rules elsewhere
